{"tid":622913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚攰呀！！！","createTime":"2018-04-09T13:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T14:20:10.000Z","uid":4517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42da2526d4f5bfa167171a97c933a63913c46f3e","tid":622913,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"每日返工都行屍走肉，雖然做嘢唔是話好辛苦，<br />\n但返到屋企已經冇咗大半條人命，日復日，年復年，好快就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵份自己鐘意做嘅工，但搵工本來已經唔易，有份正職再搵第二份就難上加難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆仲屌我話唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n我返工雖然唔洗體力勞動，但係每日疲勞轟炸，<br />\n返到屋企仲要係咁諗辦法搵份好啲嘅工，真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就嚟捱唔住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274990aef650fad56d0f784df9bfe02091520fc3","tid":622913,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:59:02.000Z","msg":"發洩完早d訓啦"},{"pid":"9a1b9964dad18744f8c06d4d0a485f4ee2e905df","tid":622913,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274990aef650fad56d0f784df9bfe02091520fc3","tid":622913,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited